title: E621: Improve code style and remove redundant comments.
message:
E621: Improve code style and remove redundant comments.

For the record:

- It's good practice to use 64-bit values (longs) to represent database
  primary keys.
- I'd rather rely on service auto-detection than use hardcoded values.
  What if Safebooru upgraded to Danbooru 2.0 and dropped support for the
  old API?
